The paper discusses the application of machine learning techniques to improve search ranking on Airbnb, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The paper specifically focuses on the use of neural networks, which is a popular topic in machine learning research and falls under several sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
